node.text: To kick off the new year we collaborated with 5 female artists from around the world to create a series of limited edition artist-designed boxes. Today we’re featuring the mastermind behind @briapaints, Bria Nicole from Texas! As a Black woman, positive representation of Black and brown people is central to her work, but the importance of self care, self love, and basking in the simple joys of life are themes all can relate to. If you’re not feeling inspired after watching this, wyd?! 💃🏽
